03:21.960 --> 03:23.120
as it's been going along,

03:23.120 --> 03:27.320
and yeah, they've got all of the packages available

03:27.320 --> 03:29.120
side-by-side, so you can take your pick

03:29.120 --> 03:31.600
where you need to take a pick.

03:31.600 --> 03:32.760
