is not compatible with anything newer than the 54 kernel,

04:12.640 --> 04:14.760
so I think it's there so that people

04:14.760 --> 04:17.920
that have got older generations Nvidia cards

04:17.920 --> 04:22.240
have still got a support root there on an LTS kernel.

04:22.240 --> 04:24.100
